Name: Hotels At Home
Description: Hotels @ Home, is an eCommerce solutions provider to many of the world?s leading hospitality brands.  They manage online retail programs for over 30 global brands where customers can buy the beds, bedding, fragrance, bath, and other products experienced during their hotel stays via our uniquely branded websites such as WestinStore.com, ShopEdition.com, and KimptonStyle.com The company manages ALL aspects of our online retail programs in-house, out of our headquarters in Fairfield, New Jersey and regional offices in Paris and Shanghai. Our experienced team designs, develops, and hosts eCommerce websites, executes digital and offline marketing campaigns, and manages procurement, warehousing, logistics, and customer service. The result of managing all aspects of our retail programs in-house is that our team is extremely cross-functional and collaborative which allows for us to achieve greater results.  We are an 18 year old company with a talented, hard-working, and experienced team that sincerely enjoys coming to work each day. We are in the fortunate position to be expanding in all areas of our business as we redevelop websites, add new clients, and execute upon our marking activations.  Additionally, we are in the midst of several foundational projects in Q4 2018 and 2019 including upgrading to a new ERP system and migrating our remaining hosted severs to AWS.  Our ERP upgrade is a fundamental project where we have been analyzing the needs of each individual department to identify ways where we can have our software facilitate their workflows to make their jobs easier and so that they can focus their efforts on higher-value tasks.  This is an ongoing multi-year project that has started in our Chinese office and is rolling out in France in 2019 and the US in 2020. Our business model is unique particularly in that we manage all aspects of our eCommerce programs in-house.  We have found that many companies tend to take a more siloed approach to job responsibilities and, due to the collaborative cross-functional nature of our business, most candidates come to us without deep knowledge in all of the various tasks for which they will be responsible.  Therefore, we tend to make personality hires rather than skills based hires and we seek to hire hard working individuals who are comfortable working as part of a team, who are accountable, detail-oriented and capable of managing complex projects, and who and are capable of learning the specific details required to lead the projects entrusted to them while possessing the critical-thinking skills necessary to be able to research and evaluate unfamiliar assignments.  We are fortunate that many of the people on our team have worked for us for us for five or more years and we are only interested in hiring people who are seeking to grow with our company and stay with us for the long term.  Please note that we are only seeking to hire people to work on-site in our office in Fairfield, New Jersey (or Paris or Shanghai).  If this type of environment is interesting for you then I would be happy to have an interview to learn more about your background and what you are looking for in a career and to tell you more about our company.  My schedule is completely packed this week but I am available for a Tuesday the 25th between 7:00 ? 11:00, Wednesday the 26th between 7:00 ? 10:00, Thursday the 27th between 7:00 am ? 11:00 am and Friday the 28th between 7:00 am ? 10:00 am. Description: National Coatings Corporation is a leading commercial roofing system manufacturer of durable, energy-efficient and environmentally friendly weatherproofing in service on hundreds of millions of square feet of commercial and industrial roofs and walls. In 1981, Rick Sexauer founded National Coatings to manufacture high-performance AcryShield coatings focusing the company on providing dedicated service and superior products based on advanced acrylic technology. From entrepreneurial roots, National Coatings now serves Fortune 500 clients in Manufacturing, Warehousing and Distribution, Commercial Property Management, Major Retailing, Entertainment and Hospitality.  Key offerings include: Coating restoration systems for extending the performance lives of asphalt based roofing, single-ply roofing, foam roofing, elastomeric roof coatings and metal roofing. Our reinforced coating membranes provide strength and durability beyond traditional roofing and repair. Premium sprayed polyurethane foam roofing (SPF) systems for re-roofs and new construction offer extra insulation and better slope-to-drain. Wall waterproofing systems using high performance elastomeric wall coatings (EWC's) have excellent color retention, bridge hairline cracks, and boast excellent resistance to dirt pick-up and wind-driven rain. National Coatings provides its market-leading systems under the AcryShield, AcryLock?, AcryPly, AcryPly-D, AcryFlex, and RenuWall names.
